imports System.Drawing imports System.Printing imports System.Drawing.Printing
Public Class Snippet
Public Shared Function getprinters() As System.String Dim drucker As String = "" Dim kassetten As String Dim tempname As String = "" Dim i, j As Integer Dim printerobj As New System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings For i = 0 To PrinterSettings.InstalledPrinters.Count - 1 kassetten = "" tempname = PrinterSettings.InstalledPrinters.Item(i) drucker = drucker + tempname + "^" printerobj.PrinterName = PrinterSettings.InstalledPrinters.Item(i) drucker = drucker.Trim + printerobj.CanDuplex.ToString + "^" drucker = drucker.Trim + printerobj.SupportsColor.ToString + "^"
For j = 0 To printerobj.PaperSources.Count - 1 If kassetten.Trim > "" Then kassetten = kassetten.Trim + ";" kassetten = kassetten.Trim + printerobj.PaperSources.Item(j).SourceName.Trim.Replace("~","") Next drucker = drucker.Trim + kassetten.Trim + "~" Next i return drucker
End Function
End Class
